definition: to attain/to reach/to amount to/to communicate/eminent
to (a place)/until (a time)/up to/to go/to arrive/(verb complement denoting completion or result of an action)

sentences.english: NH3-N and concentration of particles reached lnd standard of sewage treatment plant.
sentences.chinese: 濃度和濁度達到國家一級排放標準。

sentences.english: Only God radiates at level seven.
sentences.chinese: 只有上帝才能達到第七級。

sentences.english: Linda phoned me in on arrival so that I know she was safe and sound.
sentences.chinese: 琳達到達後給我打了電話，因而我知道她平安無事。

sentences.english: Should one renounce Nirvana oneself, in order to help others towards it first?
sentences.chinese: 人應該放棄自己的涅磐，爲了首先幫助它人達到它？

sentences.english: At the cost balance point on the institutional margin, the allocation of power achieves Pareto Optimality.
sentences.chinese: 在制度邊際成本持平處權力的配置達到帕累托最優。

sentences.english: If you do one thing each day, you'll reach your goal.
sentences.chinese: 如果你每天都做一件事，你會達到你的目標的。

sentences.english: That is, with the same cost, a better con- trolling result can be obtained.
sentences.chinese: 用相同的費用就能達到更好的控制疾病的效果。

sentences.english: It didn't reach required standards of safety and seaworthiness.
sentences.chinese: 它沒有達到安全性和適航性的規定標準。

sentences.english: Experiment results show that those approaches have good real -time performance and vivid effect.
sentences.chinese: 實驗結果表明，該算法達到了較好的實時性和真實感。

sentences.english: A dog with the correct proportions and angulation can thereby achieve static balance.
sentences.chinese: 擁有的正確比例和角度，從而達到犬隻的靜態平衡。

sentences.english: Phet reached its greatest intensity off the coast of Oman on June 3.
sentences.chinese: 6月3日，“鑽石”在阿曼沿海達到最大強度。

sentences.english: The testing results of the fabric are essentially satisfactory in wearability.
sentences.chinese: 並經織物服用性能測試，基本達到滿意的效果。

sentences.english: The abode of celibacy is attained through this plan.
sentences.chinese: 禁慾可以通過這樣的方式達到。

sentences.english: The meeting was brought to a climax by the appearance on the platform of the rebel leader.
sentences.chinese: 起義軍的領袖出現在臺上時會議達到了高潮。

sentences.english: Still greater efforts are needed before we can attain our goal .
sentences.chinese: 我們必須百尺竿頭，更進一步，才能達到目的。

sentences.english: Once the water reaches saturation , it can't take anymore.
sentences.chinese: 當達到飽和時，水將無法吸收更多的砂糖。
